Britain 's Got Talent judge Amanda Holden , 44-year-old has admitted that her traumatic childbirth experiences left her needing therapy , but have inspired her to live life to the full .
In her cover interview for the June issue ofGood Housekeeping , the mother-of-two talks about therapy that saved her after she lost one child and nearly died after having another .
Holden was diagnosed with post-traumatic stress disorder .